TITLE: Quantum Systems 05: Perturbation
	- Pre-requisitives: Quantum Mechanics 04
	- Co-requisitives: Quantum Mechanics 09


Summary of the systems
	- Time-Independent: Stark Effect, Van Der Walls Interaction
	- Variational: Ground State Helium, Hydrogen Molecule Ion, Cross Shaped Potential (Quantum Dots).
	- WKB Approximation: Gamow's Alpha Decay, Allowed energy of potential V(x) = a|x|^k, k positive. Tunneling in Stark Effect.
	- Time-Dependent: Hamiltonian turning on/off, Rotating Wave Approximation (Rabi Frequency), Magnetic Ressonance, NMR, Allowed/Forbidden Transitions, EM Thermal Field.
	- Adiabatic Approximation: 


